@startuml seq-16-admin-users
' 序列图16：管理员管理用户
title 管理员管理用户序列图

actor 管理员 as Admin
participant "admin.js" as Front
participant "my.js" as MyFront
participant "AdminController" as Ctrl
participant "UserService" as Svc
participant "UserMapper" as Mapper
database "MySQL" as DB

Admin -> MyFront: 打开"我的"页
MyFront -> MyFront: 校验userType===2显示管理入口
Admin -> Front: 点击"用户管理"
Front -> Ctrl: GET /api/admin/user/list
Ctrl -> Svc: listAllUsers()
Svc -> Mapper: selectAll()
Mapper -> DB: SELECT * FROM user
DB --> Mapper: List<User>
Mapper --> Svc: List<User>
Svc --> Ctrl: List<User>
Ctrl --> Front: {code:200, data:List}
Front --> Admin: 渲染用户列表表格

@enduml
